text: Balingen is a town in Baden-Württemberg, Germany. It is the capital of the district of Zollernalbkreis. It is located near the Swabian Alb. It is to the south of Tübingen, northeast of Villingen-Schwenningen, and southwest of Stuttgart. ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:Zollernalbkreis
